# Task 008: E2E Testing Suite

## Description
Develop a comprehensive end-to-end testing suite for the CBSC Strategy Management Dashboard, ensuring reliable functionality across all user workflows and integration points.

## Scope

### Test Framework Setup
- Playwright/Cypress configuration for cross-browser testing
- Test environment orchestration (Docker compose)
- Test data management and fixtures
- CI/CD integration for automated testing
- Visual regression testing capabilities

### Core User Workflows
- Strategy creation and management
- Parameter optimization process
- Backtest execution and analysis
- Dashboard navigation and interaction
- Alert configuration and notification testing

### Integration Testing
- WebSocket real-time updates
- API endpoint validation
- Database transaction integrity
- Third-party service integrations
- Authentication and authorization flows

### Performance Testing
- Page load time benchmarks
- Real-time update performance
- Large dataset handling
- Memory leak detection
- Mobile responsiveness validation

